  "texts": [
    "To simultaneously mine the patient similarities and the latent cross-modality relations, we design a contrastive loss to model the pairs of patients and each patient's text-visit pairs.",
    "The contributions of this work can be summarized as follows:",
    "• We distill the cross-modal knowledge from LLM to boost the health event prediction and fully exploit the LLM capability by prompting to generate augmented text.",
    "• We design a contrastive distillation loss to learn the multi-modality knowledge from teacher model and similarities between patients at the same time.",
    "• Extensive experiments are conducted on two representative health event prediction tasks to validate the effectiveness of the CKLE framework."
  ],
